commits.content:
{
  "name": "craigslist-to-json",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Chrome extension to convert Craigslist posts to JSON format",
  "main": "index.js",
  "scripts": {
    "test": "jest",
    "build": "mkdir -p dist && cp -r web_extension/chrome/* dist/ && zip -r dist/craigslist-to-json.zip dist/"
  },
  "keywords": [
    "chrome-extension",
    "craigslist",
    "json"
  ],
  "author": "",
  "license": "MIT",
  "dependencies": {},
  "devDependencies": {
    "@babel/core": "^7.21.0",
    "@babel/preset-env": "^7.20.2",
    "babel-jest": "^29.5.0",
    "jest": "^29.5.0",
    "jest-environment-jsdom": "^29.5.0",
    "puppeteer": "^19.7.3"
  }
}
